"Monday and subsequently fixed along with several related issues.  The "
"\"deny config write\" privilege coupled with admin or user and group "
"manager rights are affected combinations.  It is an uncommon way to "
"configure access as the \"deny config write\" privilege is commonly used "
"for role-based access to non-system services, e.g. captive portals."
